## USAGE INSTRUCTIONS FOR DAN

**Time to update daily:** <2 minutes
**When to update:** End of day (after final pack/dispatch)
**What you enter:**
- Units sold that day (from Fynd orders)
- Units added to stock (from production received)
- Any damaged/defective units removed

**What updates automatically:**
- Current stock level per SKU
- Days until stock-out (based on velocity)
- Low-stock alerts (when stock falls below threshold)
- Reorder recommendations (when to contact Ink Fish)

