## SHEET 2: LIVE STOCK TRACKER

**Update this sheet EVERY DAY.** Columns marked with 🔴 require manual entry. All others auto-calculate.

| Article # | Product Name | Stock (Units) 🔴 | Threshold | Days to Stockout (calc) | Reorder Status (calc) | Velocity (7-day avg) 🔴 | Notes |
|-----------|--------------|-----------------|-----------|------------------------|----------------------|------------------------|-------|
| CS-001 | Card Sticker Full (Attitude Mix) | [enter] | 50 | =[C2/(G2+0.1)] | IF(C2<=D2,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | |
| CS-002 | Card Sticker Half (Attitude Mix) | [enter] | 50 | =[C2/(G2+0.1)] | IF(C2<=D2,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | |
| KC-101 | Keychain — Bullshit Remover | [enter] | 40 | =[C3/(G3+0.1)] | IF(C3<=D3,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | Hero product — keep full |
| KC-102 | Keychain — Idiot Repellent | [enter] | 40 | =[C4/(G4+0.1)] | IF(C4<=D4,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | Hero product — keep full |
| KC-103 | Keychain — Enjoy the ShitShow | [enter] | 40 | =[C5/(G5+0.1)] | IF(C5<=D5,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | Hero product — keep full |
| KC-104 | Keychain — Straight outta F#_ks | [enter] | 40 | =[C6/(G6+0.1)] | IF(C6<=D6,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | Hero product — keep full |
| KC-201 | Keychains — Identity/Interest Mix | [enter] | 30 | =[C7/(G7+0.1)] | IF(C7<=D7,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | 10+ SKUs pooled. High SKU velocity |
| LP-301 | Lapel Pins — Original Designs (mix) | [enter] | 25 | =[C8/(G8+0.1)] | IF(C8<=D8,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | 15+ limited-run SKUs. Track by series |
| MG-401 | Fridge Magnets — Mix | [enter] | 30 | =[C9/(G9+0.1)] | IF(C9<=D9,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | 8-10 SKUs pooled |
| BND-501 | Bundle — Card Starter | [enter] | 20 | =[C10/(G10+0.1)] | IF(C10<=D10,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | Pre-packed. Lower velocity (bundling) |
| BND-502 | Bundle — No Filter Essentials | [enter] | 20 | =[C11/(G11+0.1)] | IF(C11<=D11,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | Pre-packed. Lower velocity |
| BND-503 | Bundle — Collector's Set | [enter] | 15 | =[C12/(G12+0.1)] | IF(C12<=D12,"LOW","OK") | [enter] | Premium. Lower volume expected |

**HOW TO UPDATE THIS SHEET:**

1. **Stock (Units)** — Enter the count you physically have after packing orders
2. **Velocity (7-day avg)** — Update weekly (Friday). Calculate: Total units sold in last 7 days ÷ 7
   - Example: Sold 63 card stickers in 7 days = velocity is 9 units/day
3. Other columns auto-calculate. If you see an error, check your velocity entry.

**ALERTS THAT TRIGGER REORDER:**
- ANY product shows "LOW" in **Reorder Status** column → **Contact Ink Fish immediately**
- ANY product shows ≤7 days in **Days to Stockout** → **Urgent reorder**
- Bundles stockout faster than components (higher order frequency) → Monitor BND-501 and BND-502 weekly

