## SHEET 4: REORDER TRACKING

Track all production orders with Ink Fish. Use this to forecast when stock arrives and when to expect it to run out.

| Reorder # | Date Requested | SKUs Ordered (article #s) | Quantity | Lead Time (days) | ETA Arrival | Status | Notes |
|-----------|----------------|--------------------------|----------|------------------|-------------|--------|-------|
| INK-001 | 2026-03-27 | CS-001, CS-002, KC-101/102/103/104 (10 each SKU) | 80 units | 14 | 2026-04-10 | Pending | Pre-launch initial stock |
| INK-002 | [date] | [article #s] | [qty] | [days] | [ETA] | [status] | |

**LEAD TIME REFERENCE (from Ink Fish production):**
- **Standard reorder:** 14 calendar days from order to delivery
- **Rush reorder:** 7 calendar days (10% surcharge) — use only if "Days to Stockout" shows ≤7
- **New design first run:** 21 calendar days (product design approval required)

**USE THIS TRACKER TO:**
1. Know when stock arrives so you can plan staging area
2. Forecast stock depletion: When this batch runs out = next ETA date
3. Decide "do we reorder again or kill this SKU?" — visible 14 days in advance

