## SHEET 5: COST & MARGIN TRACKING

Snapshot of profitability by collection. Updated monthly (Dan can do this on the first of the month).

| Collection | Total Units Sold (MTD) | Avg Unit Cost (₹) | Avg Selling Price (₹) | Total Revenue (₹) | Total COGS (₹) | Gross Profit (₹) | Gross Margin % | Notes |
|-----------|------------------------|-------------------|----------------------|------------------|---------------|-----------------|----------------|-------|
| Card Stickers | [#] | 10 | 160 | [calc] | [calc] | [calc] | [calc] | Entry tier. High volume |
| No Filter (Keychains) | [#] | 18 | 249 | [calc] | [calc] | [calc] | [calc] | Hero product. Lower volume, higher margin |
| Pin Edit (Lapel Pins) | [#] | 22 | 299 | [calc] | [calc] | [calc] | [calc] | Premium. Collectible. Vary by artist series |
| Supporting (Magnets + IK) | [#] | 16 | 224 | [calc] | [calc] | [calc] | [calc] | AOV builders. Mixed bag |
| Bundles | [#] | 44 | 532 | [calc] | [calc] | [calc] | [calc] | Highest margin. Gifting driver. Lower volume |

**FORMULAS:**
- Total Revenue = Total Units × Avg Selling Price
- Total COGS = Total Units × Avg Unit Cost
- Gross Profit = Total Revenue − Total COGS
- Gross Margin % = Gross Profit ÷ Total Revenue × 100

**PURPOSE:** Visible at a glance which collections are driving margin and which are just volume. Feeds into Phase 6 optimization decisions.

