## SHEET 6: STOCK VERIFICATION CHECKLIST

Weekly physical audit of inventory. Protects against loss, miscount, or shrinkage.

| Week Ending | Audited By | Article # | Expected Count | Physical Count | Variance | Notes | Signoff |
|-------------|-----------|-----------|-----------------|----------------|----------|-------|---------|
| 2026-03-27 | Dan | CS-001 | [from SHEET 2] | [count] | [diff] | [notes] | [Y/N] |
| 2026-03-27 | Dan | KC-101 | [from SHEET 2] | [count] | [diff] | [notes] | [Y/N] |

**WHEN:** Friday end of day, before weekend
**WHAT:** Count every SKU physically. Compare to SHEET 2 "Stock" column.
**WHY:** Catches data entry errors, damaged inventory not yet logged, or loss in transit
**IF VARIANCE > 5%:** Investigate. Update SHEET 2 and SHEET 3 with the correct count.

