## NOTES FOR IMPLEMENTATION

**Import this into Google Sheets or Excel:**
- All formulas should translate directly to either platform
- Conditional formatting (GREEN for "OK", RED for "LOW") makes alerts visual
- Set up mobile access so Dan can check stock from the Ink Fish warehouse or while at the post office

**For future scaling (Phase 5-6):**
- This tracker will feed into demand forecasting (Phase 6 optimization)
- Collect enough weekly velocity data (4+ weeks) to smooth out launch volatility
- After Day 30: Analyze high-velocity SKUs vs. slow-movers → Drop 2 recommendations

**If Dan hires ops help in Phase 5+:**
- This tracker is the accountability document
- Any team member can see: What's in stock, what needs reordering, what's profitable
- Reduces friction, increases trust
